513418333128849698.Text: Sure. Thash what I said? Did I stutter or shomethin? Talking. Mudcrab. Merchant. Read my lips. Ehr. Mouthparts? Read my mouthparts? Shomethin ain't right. But never mind. Jush one-a life's little myshteries. So. You gonna buy shomethin? Or sit here jawin' all day.

31150128011228912388.Text: M'aiq has heard of this. They've got all the money. Mudcrabs taking over everything. They already run Pelagiad.
